"Mae Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov wedi achosi anaf, niwed a cholled i deulu a ffrindiau Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, a Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", meddai'r hysbysiad bwriad.
